PN,30804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1784236711
OL,3,CUnder-16s in England to be banned from
OL,4,Cbuying energy drinks
OL,6,FThe ban follows a consultation which
OL,7,Freceived nearly 1,100 responses from
OL,8,Fbusinesses, public health
OL,9,Forganisations, enforcement bodies and
OL,10,Fmembers of the public, with strong
OL,11,Fsupport for introducing an age
OL,12,Frestriction.
OL,14,FEducation Minister Olivia Bailey said:
OL,15,F"This ban will protect children from
OL,16,Fhigh-caffeine energy drinks that
OL,17,Fundermine their health and focus in
OL,18,Fthe classroom, so they can make the
OL,19,Fmost of all the exciting opportunities
OL,20,Fahead of them.
OL,26,@wD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
