OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1784236711
OL,3,CUnder-16s in England to be banned from
OL,4,Cbuying energy drinks
OL,6,F"It will go hand in hand with our
OL,7,Foverhaul of school food for the first
OL,8,Ftime in over a decade, to ensure
OL,9,Fchildren across the country have
OL,10,Fdelicious, nutritious food that helps
OL,11,Fthem thrive."
OL,13,FRetailers themselves will be
OL,14,Fresponsible for ensuring these drinks
OL,15,Fare not sold to under-16s, while local
OL,16,Fauthorities will enforce the ban.
OL,17,FBusinesses that break the law face
OL,18,Ffines of up to #2,500.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1784236711
OL,3,CUnder-16s in England to be banned from
OL,4,Cbuying energy drinks
OL,6,FMinisters plan to bring in the ban
OL,7,Fthrough secondary legislation under
OL,8,Fthe Food Safety Act 1990, with the
OL,9,Fmeasures set to take effect in April
OL,10,F2027, subject to parliamentary
OL,11,Fapproval.
OL,13,FKatharine Jenner, Executive Director
OL,14,Fof the Obesity Health Alliance, called
OL,15,Fthe ban "a hugely popular policy,
OL,16,Fbacked by parents, health
OL,17,Fprofessionals and the public."
OL,19,FShe said it was a "vital step towards
OL,20,Fprotecting children's health".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
