PN,30807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1784236711
OL,3,CUnder-16s in England to be banned from
OL,4,Cbuying energy drinks
OL,6,F"Strong evidence links high-caffeine
OL,7,Fenergy drinks to anxiety, poor sleep,
OL,8,Freduced concentration and harm to
OL,9,Flearning and wellbeing - restricting
OL,10,Fsales to children at a vital time in
OL,11,Ftheir life is just common-sense.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
