PN,30808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1784236711
OL,3,CUnder-16s in England to be banned from
OL,4,Cbuying energy drinks
OL,6,F"Children in more deprived communities
OL,7,Fare disproportionately affected.
OL,8,FExtending the ban across shops,
OL,9,Fvending machines and online sales will
OL,10,Fcreate a fair, consistent system for
OL,11,Fretailers and families. After years of
OL,12,Fdelay, the Government must now secure
OL,13,Fapproval, support effective
OL,14,Fenforcement and ensure the ban starts
OL,15,Fpromptly in April 2027."
